OL,4,C#1.9bn of Covid loan losses, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe bounce back loan scheme was set up
OL,7,Fin the early days of the Covid-19
OL,8,Flockdowns when businesses across the
OL,9,Fcountry were forced to close or faced
OL,10,Fa drop-off in demand.
OL,12,FIt provided loans of up to #50,000 per
OL,13,Fbusiness, and were available to most
OL,14,FUK firms without the usual credit and
OL,15,Faffordability checks in order to be
OL,16,Fissued more quickly.
