OL,3,CGovernment 'passive' in recovering
OL,4,C#1.9bn of Covid loan losses, MPs warn
OL,6,FHowever, the Department for Business
OL,7,Fand Trade (DBT) estimated that total
OL,8,Flosses due to fraud on the bounce back
OL,9,Floan scheme will be at least #1.9
OL,10,Fbillion ` with the figure likely to be
OL,11,Fhigher as not all fraudulent cases had
OL,12,Fbeen identified.
OL,14,FThe DBT also said that some #130
OL,15,Fmillion worth of losses had so far
OL,16,Fbeen recovered from the bounce back
OL,17,Fscheme ` but said it was not possible
OL,18,Fto identify how much related to
OL,19,Fborrowers contracting them
OL,20,Ffraudulently.
