OL,6,FThe Government guaranteed to cover any
OL,7,Flosses incurred by lenders on loans
OL,8,Fwhich could not be repaid when the
OL,9,Fscheme began.
OL,11,FIt has nonetheless withdrawn its
OL,12,Fbacking on #367 million worth of loans
OL,13,Fwhere it felt lenders have not done
OL,14,Fall it should have done ` meaning
OL,15,Fbanks foot the bill, rather than
OL,16,Ftaxpayers.
