OL,3,CGovernment 'passive' in recovering
OL,4,C#1.9bn of Covid loan losses, MPs warn
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Starling Bank said
OL,7,Fit had agreed to remove the Government
OL,8,Fguarantee on a group of loans that had
OL,9,Fpotential issues ` leading it to put
OL,10,Faside some #28 million.
OL,12,FBut the PAC said the broader guarantee
OL,13,Fmeant there was a lack of incentive
OL,14,Ffor banks to recover taxpayers' money.
OL,16,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,17,Fof the committee, criticised
OL,18,F"passivity" in the Government's
OL,19,Fapproach.
