OL,6,F"DBT were unable to tell us if even
OL,7,Fthe tiny fraction of that sum
OL,8,Frecovered was in fact even related to
OL,9,Ffraud," he said.
OL,11,F"Indeed, relying on government-backed
OL,12,Flenders to recover losses, who thus
OL,13,Flack any incentive to pursue lost
OL,14,Ffunds, has been a dangerously flat-
OL,15,Ffooted approach.
OL,17,F"Now that the Insolvency Service has
OL,18,Ftaken over responsibility for viable
OL,19,Fcases, we look forward to hearing how
OL,20,Fit fares where others have failed."
